BEGIN_TEXT

Let \( f(x) =  \tan ($a x) \). $BR$BR
\( f'(x) = \) \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR$BR
\( f'($x1) = \) \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR$BR
\( f''( x ) = \) \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR$BR
\( f''( $x1 ) = \) \{ans_rule(20) \} 

END_TEXT

